    1. `A p` is almost invariant under the ergodic map `y ‚Ü¶ p ‚Ä¢ y`
    2. `B p` is almost invariant under the ergodic map `y ‚Ü¶ p ‚Ä¢ y + 1/p`
    3. `C p` is invariant under the map `y ‚Ü¶ y + 1/p`
